cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.PL

This paper is about optimization-based falsification of hybrid systems, which involves using stochastic optimization algorithms to search for error input. This topic is closely related to the field of control systems (cs.SY), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) due to the use of optimization algorithms. The paper also discusses the use of time-dependent signals, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
